&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>shadowsocks在centos编译安装</title><link>https://fliaping.github.io/Blog/how-to-compile-and-install-shadowsocks-on-centos/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Dec 2015 07:23:17 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://fliaping.github.io/Blog/how-to-compile-and-install-shadowsocks-on-centos/</guid><description>&lt;p>现在新疆把python 的软件库都封了，pip都安不上，那只好自己编译安装了。系统为centos6 x64
